<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='516000' id='t-516000'>And I have learned so much</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='518000' id='t-518000'>from Chris and Kevin</span>
