<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='568000' id='t-568000'>My own work focuses</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='570000' id='t-570000'>on making philanthropy more effective</span>
