<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='576000' id='t-576000'>At Acumen Fund, we take philanthropic resources</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='579000' id='t-579000'>and we invest what we call patient capital --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='581000' id='t-581000'>money that will invest in entrepreneurs who see the poor</span>
